des:
Stress Release is the Alexa skill that offers guided sessions whenever you need relief from tension and stress. With over 10 unique sessions, each lasting 10 minutes, and featuring a variety of calming voices and soothing background sounds, this skill is crafted to help both your body and mind achieve a state of complete relaxation.

Unlock Pro Features to enjoy:

• Guided sessions with professional, soothing voices
• A selection of background sounds ideal for relaxation
• Unlimited access with no restrictions
• Regularly updated stress-relief programs
• Full access to all session lengths

We value your feedback to help us improve and provide the ultimate relaxation experience.

Enjoy your journey to stress relief!
